OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA clear
OL,6,Fevening for many. Some cloud makes
OL,7,Fprogress inland, but it will remain
OL,8,Fclear along the south coast. A light
OL,9,Fto gentle northeasterly breeze,
OL,10,Fstaying windier along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FPatchy cloud soon clears to
OL,13,Fgive a bright and sunny day. Sunshine
OL,14,Fperhaps turning a little hazy by the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Remaining breezy along the
OL,16,Fcoast with a brisk northeasterly wind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
