OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSettled
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells. Feeling cooler by
OL,7,Fthe weekend than in previous days with
OL,8,Fa northerly breeze, though daytime
OL,9,Ftemperatures likely remaining slightly
OL,10,Fabove average.
